  <summary date="2019-07-19T21:24:14Z" status="Introduced in House">Physician Education for Fistula Treatment Act

This bill authorizes the John E. Fogarty International Center for Advanced Study in the Health Sciences, which is part of the National Institutes of Health, to support training programs for obstetrician-gynecologists and sub-specialists in urogynecology in least developed countries; the center must also develop a strategy to address physician shortages in such countries.</summary>
